ss=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBe water my friends <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n524謹記適時保持兩米距離排排企<br />\n我鍾意排隊等巴士<br />\n排隊食黃店<br />\n企定定睇熱鬧<br />\n地少人多，閒閒地都<br />\n1000人、10000人、100000人、1000000人<br />\n隊形痴埋一齊都好正常<br />\n<br />\n文宣係咩？紙囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加卡版、咪變硬卡紙囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天口熱、撥下涼姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n狗狗鍾意票控咪由得佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抄佢老母票、抄到佢天荒地老<br />\n彌敦道出九龍大老山隧道獅子山入口再出港島太平山<br />\n同我罰抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抄到無紙<br />\n呃佢老母ot錢<br />\n法庭忙到甩轆<br />\n最後原來得個吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜都唔洗罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鍾意講咩玩咩都係自由意志<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\np牌嘅價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，借個靚位黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個秒獲負皮，明明得我自彈自唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多一個人理就即刻放負一隻<br />\n<br />\n證明咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吖媽我得左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五毛加持嘅大絕<br />\n使出香港人大技-人海戰術<br />\n排排企食果果<br />\n破佢老母限聚令<br />\n<br />\n兄弟努力 各自爬山<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2031264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2031264</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n同意請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反其道而行，先係破局<br />\n同狗玩數字遊戲無意思<br />\n要玩就黎舖曬冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afed17bbd2b07bfc3d1392f6a438d5d82fbd14ec","tid":2031690,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:42:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f034a15e26c1608f6b2462be300cdcdc9e90b7b","tid":2031690,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dffeee90240f8de6927448916d03b7836b66b462","tid":2031690,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867562e3985193c85bc40e33d39511104c425ff9","tid":2031690,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b80fb36ca75a0157a87b99112124992ebab3c4c","tid":2031690,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:47:22.000Z","msg":"正唔正先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}